title: MORE OF THE SCORE - OCT. 2
text:
MORE OF THE SCORE - OCT. 2 
By DONOVAN KLEIN October 3, 2015 Updated Oct 3, 2015 at 1:27 AM EDT 
FORT WAYNE, IND (21ALIVE) - In the October 3 episode of More of the Score, 21Alive's Tommy Schoegler and AWP's Antoine Taylor break down Dwenger and Snider's big wins and how they will match-up next week for one of the biggest game's of the year. 
Also, the guys talk about Bellmont's win and how long their hot streak could last. Bellmont's head coach Larry Getts also calls into the show to talk about his teams expectations.
